Movie: Love Has Won: The Cult of Mother God
Review: don’t take ecstasy to subconsciously cope with unresolved childhood trauma—you may start a cult and embark on a galactic suicide mission led by robin williams’ ghost.this cult is one of the more hilariously batshit, nonsensical ones out there and that itself makes it one of the best -and most bleak- examples of the things broken people will believe, and the irrational answers they will cling to, if they are desperate enough.
